{
    "text": "\ud83d\udccdTransylvania, Romania  Where is your favourite place to visit?\ud83c\uddf7\ud83c\uddf4\u2665 Tag all your travel besties\u2757  Follow \u2014> @escapetoeurope  Follow \u2014> @escapetoeurope  \ud83e\udde0It\u2019s home to the world\u2019s heaviest building. Bucharest\u2019s vast Palace of the Parliament, begun during the final years of Nicolae Ceau\u0219escu\u2019s rule and not finished until 1997 (seven years after his death), is 240 metres long, 270 metres wide, 86 metres high (12 storeys), and cost a staggering \u20ac3 billion (\u00a32.5bn) to build\u2757  Credit to @bokehm0n and @map_of_europe   #escapetoeurope #europe #travel #travels #travelblogger #earth #placestovisit #dreamdestinations #discovertheglobe #travelaway #travelenthusiast #travelforlife #traveldestinations #travelblog #travelblogger #travellingthroughtheworld #beautifuldestinations #traveloften #picoftheday #travelineurope #travelaway #topdestinations #travelstagram #travelphotography #instaeurope #rom\u00e2nia #romania #romaniatravel #transylvania #romania\ud83c\uddf9\ud83c\udde9",
